Subject: [PATCH] windows.ui: Add stubs for RadialController classes.

---
 dlls/windows.ui/Makefile.in                |   2 +
 dlls/windows.ui/classes.idl                |   6 +
 dlls/windows.ui/main.c                     |   9 +
 dlls/windows.ui/private.h                  |   5 +
 dlls/windows.ui/radialcontroller.c         | 332 +++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/windows.ui/radialcontrollermenuitem.c | 143 +++++++++
 6 files changed, 497 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 dlls/windows.ui/radialcontroller.c
